oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Market and Main Street, Looking East, Jackson, Tenn.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: View of Market and Main Street in Jackson, Tennessee. Shows the north side business area, multi-storied buildings (including the First National Bank in foreground), automobiles, and pedestrians.
Jackson, Tennessee is the county seat of Madison County. At one time, Jackson was the second largest trade center of West Tennessee.
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson, L.D.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Streets; Buildings; Automobiles; Stores & shops; Banks
